original: Corenius, Karl Ragnar Nison, disponent, Huskvarna, f. 29/6/03 i Huskvarna av dir. Emil Nilsson o. Karin Carlson. G. 37 m. Daisy Bergen. Barn: Ann-Louise f. 38, Carin 40, Per 43. — Realex. 20, handrinst. i Hamburg o. London 21-24. Disp. o. v. verkst. dir. v. A-B Husqvarna Borstfabr. sed. 35. Led. av styr. f. Sv. träind :förb., led. av styr. f. A-B Gbgs Hand :banks kont. ’i Huskvarna sed. 40 o. dess ordf.
translated: Corenius, Karl Ragnar Nison, manager, Huskvarna, born June 29th, 1903 in Huskvarna to director Emil Nilsson and Karin Carlson. Married in 1937 to Daisy Bergen. Children: Ann-Louise born in 1938, Carin in 1940, and Per in 1943. Completed Realexamen in 1920, worked as a clerk in Hamburg and London from 1921-1924. Became manager and vice managing director of A-B Husqvarna Borstfabr. in 1935. Member of the board for the Swedish Wood Industry Association and the board for A-B Gbgs Hand: banks kont. in Huskvarna since 1940 and its chairman.
